627
01:15:19,033 --> 01:15:22,858
Christa, you want to play Lenin
or his beloved mother?

628
01:15:22,893 --> 01:15:24,484
you can choose either one.

629
01:15:25,645 --> 01:15:28,393
I think I'd better leave you guys alone
I am going to take a nap

630
01:15:37,027 --> 01:15:38,923
you should be careful

631
01:15:39,927 --> 01:15:43,918
the less people know, the better.
the National Security is desperate

632
01:15:49,710 --> 01:15:53,140
I also brought you some presents

633
01:15:57,334 --> 01:15:58,910
as cute as the cake

634
01:15:59,398 --> 01:16:01,063
I have a typewriter

635
01:16:01,073 --> 01:16:08,767
the National Security will
search everything here

636
01:16:08,802 --> 01:16:12,467
it's not for fun
it's also for Paul's safety

637
01:16:14,881 --> 01:16:18,750
unfortunately only red ink is available for this type of pocket-sized typewriter

638
01:16:18,785 --> 01:16:21,617
you can switch to black after you finish the red.

639
01:16:21,652 --> 01:16:23,272
who knows if that's gotta happen

640
01:16:23,307 --> 01:16:27,326
you have to hide it whenever necessary

641
01:16:28,224 --> 01:16:31,013
- ok, I promise to keep it safe
- it is a serious matter

642
01:16:32,066 --> 01:16:36,504
I don't want you all get into trouble because of this typewriter

643
01:16:36,539 --> 01:16:39,317
only the three of us know about this typewriter

644
01:16:41,669 --> 01:16:43,703
are you sure your appartment is safe?

645
01:16:43,910 --> 01:16:45,185
yes

646
01:16:46,868 --> 01:16:50,594
