647
01:16:51,242 --> 01:16:53,605
good, then let's wait for the hugh impact from this article

648
01:16:56,715 --> 01:16:58,937
This bottle of wine is real!

649
01:17:00,412 --> 01:17:05,035
Cheers! For revealing the truth
of DDR to every German!

650
01:17:11,546 --> 01:17:14,899
- cheers!
