673
01:18:52,539 --> 01:18:55,181
but be careful
don't let him notice

674
01:18:55,216 --> 01:18:58,289
don't have any contact with him

675
01:18:59,061 --> 01:19:03,428
don't be emotional,
don't reveal any personal information, even in the report

676
01:19:03,463 --> 01:19:05,805
don't leave him any trace that he might write into his book in the future

677
01:19:06,878 --> 01:19:09,369
you will be free in 10 months

678
01:19:10,385 --> 01:19:11,467
completely free

