01:20:58,903 --> 01:21:01,163
write a report for me on this

707
01:21:01,595 --> 01:21:04,431
make change on the reasons accordingly

708
01:21:09,115 --> 01:21:10,746
wait

709
01:21:13,565 --> 01:21:14,595
one more thing

710
01:21:15,513 --> 01:21:18,826
we are not at school, what we do is not for a high score

711
01:21:18,861 --> 01:21:20,278
it is for the people

712
01:21:38,862 --> 01:21:41,565
agents watch everything on the street,
just like mad dogs

713
01:21:42,041 --> 01:21:44,273
on average, a man buys 2.3 pairs of shoes each year

714
